he kept staring at the receipt.

40
00:02:02.005 --> 00:02:03.872
I said, "What's wrong?"

41
00:02:03.919 --> 00:02:08.176
He said, "Isn't $1,350 too
much for eating chicken?"

42
00:02:08.294 --> 00:02:10.708
I said, "What? That's ridiculous!"

43
00:02:10.716 --> 00:02:14.919
