45
00:02:19.311 --> 00:02:21.450
It's because you can't
read so well anymore!

46
00:02:21.490 --> 00:02:23.739
How did you come up with that math?

47
00:02:23.810 --> 00:02:26.270
No, the receipt said 135 dollars.

48
00:02:27.193 --> 00:02:30.263
I was drunk, and thought
it said 1,350 dollars.

49
00:02:30.288 --> 00:02:31.349
I was just drunk.

50
00:02:31.404 --> 00:02:33.786
