59
00:02:57.638 --> 00:03:00.044
Nothing at all, I'm sure!

60
00:03:00.185 --> 00:03:02.231
But honestly,

61
00:03:02.255 --> 00:03:05.513
I don't have any problem with
my eyesight for normal things.

62
00:03:05.537 --> 00:03:08.333
- But sometimes I can't see clearly.
- You know why?

63
