00:49:57.227 --> 00:50:01.284
It would've been funny if Park
Geun-hyung acted like that father.

1041
00:50:02.847 --> 00:50:04.854
- I'm dizzy.
- I bet you're dizzy.

1042
00:50:05.082 --> 00:50:08.863
He knew if he did something, it would
finally make my emotions comes through.

1043
00:50:08.988 --> 00:50:10.541
- A knock on the head!
- No.

1044
00:50:10.566 --> 00:50:11.814
Where did he hit you?

