00:50:11.840 --> 00:50:15.026
He told me to try harder. I think
Ho-dong might do this a lot.

1046
00:50:15.051 --> 00:50:19.402
- I got it! - I think Sang-yeob's answers
are simple. He hit you on your back.

1047
00:50:19.457 --> 00:50:21.144
- That's what I thought.
- You got it!

1048
00:50:21.169 --> 00:50:22.793
You see? I told you!

1049
00:50:22.818 --> 00:50:24.369
Was the question too hard?

