00:50:24.394 --> 00:50:26.971
- No, everyone knew the answer.
- Everyone knew already?

1051
00:50:26.996 --> 00:50:31.199
Did he hit you on the back, rub
your back or pat you on the back?

1052
00:50:31.543 --> 00:50:35.480
Park Geun-hyung and I were
talking about the scene and...

